title: Kim Jong Un's sister takes centre stage at Pyeongchang
text:
Kim Jong Un's sister takes centre stage at Pyeongchang 1:05pm GMT - 01:46 
Kim Jong Un's sister, Kim Yo Jung, is part of a North Korean delegation heading to the Winter Olympics in South Korea - raising concerns that the North is trying to use the event as propaganda. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
